Illustrations in this directory are derived from OpenMoji.

Source: OpenMoji — the open-source emoji and icon project (https://openmoji.org)
Original license: Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International
  (CC BY-SA 4.0) — https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

These files are ADAPTATIONS: the OpenMoji source SVGs have been recolored
(palette-remapped to a muted warm set) and optimized. Because CC BY-SA 4.0
includes a ShareAlike term, these adaptations are distributed under the same
license, CC BY-SA 4.0.

Attribution (as surfaced in the app's About overlay):
  "Illustrations: OpenMoji — CC BY-SA 4.0, colors modified"

Placeholder note: some SVGs here are hand-drawn placeholders in the OpenMoji
flat style pending an art audit (see scripts/fetch-art.mjs). Once replaced by
recolored OpenMoji sources, the attribution above applies to them in full.
